# Streamlit App Walkthrough (Smoothed & Stable)

## Summary
The app now uses **Motion Smoothing** to remove jitter and shaky lines.

## Improvements
- **Anti-Jitter**: A smoothing filter (EMA) keeps the points stable even if the camera is noisy.
- **Threshold**: 0.10 (Balanced).

## Configuration
- **Sensitivity**: Balanced.
- **Smoothing**: Active (Alpha 0.7).

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
